responses.question2: Video is essential because I learned to see patterns in the data based on video, and learned to associate what patterns in the data corresponded with which events in the video to make identifying events easier.
responses.question3: Data is necessary because it reveals events you might not be able to see such as when someone is blocking the camera.
responses.question4: Video is easier than data. A little more time to get familiar with things would be good.
